OL,3,CAA fined #4.2m and ordered to refund
OL,4,Clearner drivers over hidden fees
OL,6,FThe AA has been fined #4.2 million by
OL,7,Fthe UK competition watchdog and
OL,8,Fordered to refund thousands of
OL,9,Fcustomers over illegal 'drip-pricing'
OL,10,Fat two of its driving schools .
OL,12,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,13,F(CMA) said the AA Driving School and
OL,14,FBSM Driving School did not include a
OL,15,Fmandatory #3 booking fee in upfront
OL,16,Fprices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
