FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776294181
OL,3,CAA fined #4.2m and ordered to refund
OL,4,Clearner drivers over hidden fees
OL,6,FAdvertising part of a product or
OL,7,Fservice's cost upfront, only to reveal
OL,8,Fhidden fees later in the checkout
OL,9,Fprocess, is known as drip-pricing,
OL,10,Fwhich was banned in the UK last year.
OL,12,FThe AA is the first to be handed a
OL,13,Fpenalty by the CMA for breach of
OL,14,Fconsumer law since it was handed new
OL,15,Fenforcement powers under the Digital
OL,16,FMarkets, Competition and Consumers Act.
OL,18,FThe amount repaid to individuals will
OL,19,Fvary depending on how many lesson
OL,20,Fpackages they bought, with the average
OL,21,Fbeing about #9.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776294181
OL,3,CAA fined #4.2m and ordered to refund
OL,4,Clearner drivers over hidden fees
OL,6,FThis will total more than #760,000.
OL,7,FThe refunds and fine combined will
OL,8,Falmost be #5 million.
OL,10,FCMA chief executive Sarah Cardell
OL,11,Fsaid: "If a fee is mandatory, the law
OL,12,Fis clear: it must be included in the
OL,13,Fprice from the very start ` not added
OL,14,Fat checkout ` so consumers always know
OL,15,Fwhat they need to pay.
OL,26,@sD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776294181
OL,3,CAA fined #4.2m and ordered to refund
OL,4,Clearner drivers over hidden fees
OL,6,F"At a time when people are watching
OL,7,Fevery pound, dripped fees can tip the
OL,8,Fbalance. And when it comes to
OL,9,Fsomething as important ` and costly `
OL,10,Fas learning to drive, people deserve
OL,11,Fclarity.
OL,13,F"With our new powers, it will never
OL,14,Fpay to break the law or treat
OL,15,Fconsumers unfairly. Where the rules
OL,16,Fare ignored, we'll step in to put
OL,17,Fthings right."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
