OL,3,CAA fined #4.2m and ordered to refund
OL,4,Clearner drivers over hidden fees
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for AA driving schools
OL,12,Fsaid: "Although the #3 booking fee was
OL,13,Fmade clear to customers prior to their
OL,14,Fpurchase, we acknowledge it should
OL,15,Fhave also been displayed at the start
OL,16,Fof the online booking journey.
OL,18,F"Having listened to the regulator, we
OL,19,Fmade immediate changes to our website
OL,20,Fto make the #3 booking fee more
OL,21,Fprominent.
OL,26,@tD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
