PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776294181
OL,3,CAA fined #4.2m and ordered to refund
OL,4,Clearner drivers over hidden fees
OL,6,F"We are now refunding all relevant
OL,7,Fcustomers. Whilst we are disappointed
OL,8,Fwith the outcome of the investigation,
OL,9,Fwe have fully co-operated with the CMA
OL,10,Fthroughout and would emphasise that
OL,11,Fprotecting consumer rights has been
OL,12,Fcentral to our business for more than
OL,13,F120 years."
OL,15,FThe CMA said affected customers do not
OL,16,Fneed to take any action, adding that
OL,17,Fthe AA Driving School or BSM Driving
OL,18,FSchool will write to them stating that
OL,19,Fthe money will be automatically
OL,20,Frefunded onto the card they used to
OL,21,Fpay for lessons.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@KO]
