OL,3,CAA fined #4.2m and ordered to refund
OL,4,Clearner drivers over hidden fees
OL,6,FIf that is not possible, they will be
OL,7,Fsent a cheque.
OL,9,FIn 2023, the Department for Business
OL,10,Fand Trade found nearly half of online
OL,11,Fbusinesses used dripped fees, with
OL,12,Fconsumers spending up to #3.5 billion
OL,13,Fper year as a result.
